Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.81,0:24:19.60,Noichuyen,SHIGARAKI,0,0,0,,Hôm nay là mèo cái à?{Today's fluff is a lady cat, huh?}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.60,0:24:20.84,Noichuyen,KOHINA,0,0,0,,Con cái à?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.84,0:24:22.96,Noichuyen,SHIGARAKI,0,0,0,,Ờ, chú nhìn phát biết ngay.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.96,0:24:23.99,Noichuyen,KOHINA,0,0,0,,Đúng là thú tính.{You lewd beast.}
